<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV11">
<l>ariyaṉa yāmiṉṟu kāṇkiṉ ṟaṉakaṇṇaṉ viṇṇaṉaiyāy</l>
<l>periyaṉa kātam poruṭkō piriveṉa ñālameytaṟ</l>
<l>kuriyaṉa veṇmuttum paimpoṉṉu mēntiyō rōkuṭaṅkai</l>
<l>periyaṉa keṇṭaik kulamivai yōvantu pērkiṉṟavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Precious are those things we see today: when we said ‘you who are like</l>
<l>Kaṇṇaṉ’s heaven, will it be long miles, separation for wealth?’,</l>
<l>one is the palm, ah, offering white pearls, fit to obtain the world, and green gold,</l>
<l>[one is] these [eyes], ah, a big family of Keṇṭai fish that come [and] go.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
